{"tid":1955532,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"EVERGLOW有人疑中肺炎","createTime":"2020-04-02T13:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T16:19:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"98866cb7096d3bdccbeb8e319075d8bf66898abf","tid":1955532,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"韓國首爾特別市江南區內，2日確診新冠肺炎陽性的四位海外入境者中，包含一位與成員們美巡EVERLASTING TOUR in USA活動軌跡高度重合的確診者。<br />\n<br />\n據韓方新聞報道，在江南區某企划社工作的23歲女性上月3日至15日在美國出差，從美國新澤西出發，乘大韓航空KE082航班15日到達韓國首爾仁川機場，27日有發熱症狀，但吃藥後有所好轉。本月1日在江南區保健所接受了檢查，2日上午被判定為陽性。(naver新聞大意)<br />\n<br />\n我們對此次確診新冠肺炎陽性的患者表示遺憾與同情，希望她能夠早日康復。另外希望我們的EG們以及公司職員都可以安全健康，也請各位粉絲朋友們在疫情期間要做好防護措施。<br />\n<br />\n在此中首希望大家能對今日電台節目取消一事表示理解。"},{"pid":"1c271b1dc18e8b935b73c9c9c49ad8df522f7bf0","tid":1955532,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"怡人小支支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/